column14: TRVN so healthy QT study expected to start no later than end of June top line data in Q4 for Oli this includes the two nonclinical items FDA asked to address This is the clear path for resubmission as they stated Figure it will take them another month or two to put together the resubmission this will also be during holidays so probably resubmit in 2020 FDA via Center of Drug Evaluation and Research CDER will respond within 30 days to the resubmission stating that it is a complete submission that addresses the CRL or if it is deficient If it is complete in addressing everything in CRL then CDER will communicate in their response whether this is a Class 1 or Class 2 resubmission Class 1 is 2 months from receipt date class 2 is 6 months
